<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "1D">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "04">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B1406027" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Valve and Cylinder Head Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B1406026">Valve and Cylinder Head Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B1406027001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove venturi plug (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B140034.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "64.914mm" ver = "01" gw = "140" gh = "167"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Place disassembled parts except valve stem seal and valve guide in order so that they can be installed in their original position.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
To facilitate servicing cylinder head, remove injectors and exhaust manifold from cylinder head.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using special tools (A) and (B) compress valve spring and then remove valve cotters (1) also using special tool (C).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D014">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-14510">
09916–14510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D015">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-14522">
09916–14522
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D016">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-84511">
09916–84511
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140093.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "104.340mm" ver = "01" gw = "159" gh = "279"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Release special tools (Valve lifter), and remove spring retainer and valve spring.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove valve from combustion chamber side.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove valve stem seal (1) and valve spring seat (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140094.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.000mm" ver = "01" gw = "161" gh = "128"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using special tool, remove valve guide from combustion chamber side to valve spring side.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D017">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-44310">
09916–44310
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140095.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.873mm" ver = "01" gw = "150" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B1406027002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B1406028">Valve and Valve Guide Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B1406029">Cylinder Head Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B1406031">Valve Spring Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Before installing valve guide into cylinder head, ream guide hole with special tool (10.5 mm reamer) so as to remove burrs and make it truly round.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D018">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-34542">
09916–34542
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D019">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-37320">
09916–37320
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140096.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.990mm" ver = "01" gw = "198" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using special tools, install new valve guide to cylinder head as follows.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D020">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-57330">
09916–57330
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D021">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-56011">
09916–56011
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not reuse valve guide. Install new oversized valve guide.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Intake and exhaust valve guides are identical.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Uniformly heat cylinder head uniformly to a temperature of 80 to 100 &#176;C (176 to 212 &#176;F) so that it will not be distorted, and drive new valve guide into its hole with special tools.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Install new valve guide until special tool contacts cylinder head.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
After installation, make sure that valve guide protrudes from cylinder head by specified dimension “a”.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<spec>
<title>
Valve guide protrusion (In and Ex)
</title>
<ptxt>
“a”: 11.0 – 11.5 mm (0.4331 – 0.4528 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140097.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "65.986mm" ver = "01" gw = "185" gh = "170"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ream valve guide bore with special tool.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Clean away shavings from reamed hole.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D022">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-34542">
09916–34542
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D023">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-34570">
09916–34570
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140096.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.990mm" ver = "01" gw = "198" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install valve spring seat to cylinder head.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install new valve stem seal (1) to valve guide.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
After applying engine oil to valve stem seal and spindle of special tool (B), fit valve stem seal to spindle, and then install valve stem seal to valve guide by pushing special tool by hand.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
After installation, check that valve stem seal is properly fixed to valve guide.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
When installing, never tap or hit special tool with a hammer or the like. Install valve stem seal to guide only by pushing special tool by hand. Tapping or hitting special tool may cause damage to valve stem seal.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D024">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09917-98221">
09917–98221
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D025">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-57330">
09916–57330
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140098.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "74.834mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "195"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply engine oil to valve stem seal, valve guide bore and valve stem.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install valve to valve guide.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140099.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.990mm" ver = "01" gw = "178" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install valve spring and spring retainer.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Each valve spring has top end (large-pitch end (1)) and bottom end (small-pitch end (2)). Be sure to position spring in place with its bottom end (small-pitch end) facing the bottom (valve spring seat side).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "36.940mm" ver = "01" gw = "60" gh = "88"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.310in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.749in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[a]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Valve spring retainer side
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Paint mark
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[b]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Valve spring seat side
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Use special tools to compress valve spring and fit two valve cotters (1) into groove in valve stem.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
When compressing the valve spring, be careful not to damage inside surface of tappet installing hole.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D026">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-14510">
09916–14510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D027">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-14522">
09916–14522
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L1D028">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09916-84511">
09916–84511
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140101.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.990mm" ver = "01" gw = "166" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install venturi plug (1) and tighten venturi plug to specified torque.
</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T1D018">
<t-part>
Venturi plug
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
3.5
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
0.36
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
2.5
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B140035.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "64.914mm" ver = "01" gw = "140" gh = "167"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install fuel injectors. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B1706008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install exhaust manifold. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B1B06002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
